-=Installation=-
Installation is easy, simply drop the .bsp and .nav file into your cstrike/maps folder. 

-=Personal Note=-
I made this map as to test and work with more features with hammer, I aspire to one day become a true level designer for a nice big company, i'm always working more and more in hammer and I'd appreciate any help anyone offer's me. Thank you and I hope you all enjoy my map.
